headline: FedEx begins its first direct Singapore-US air cargo service
summary: FedEx has added another link to its deferred air cargo network with regularly scheduled all-cargo flights from Singapore to Alaska. The post FedEx begins its first direct Singapore-US air cargo service appeared first on FreightWaves.
